net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.external

Interface ExternalAction

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SaveResourceExternalAction, URLExternalAction, ViewResourceExternalAction

    public interface ExternalAction
    Base class for all external commands. An external command is a generic way to perform some action outside of the MIWT framework. It is up to the medium layer to decide how to perform the action.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
